1
00:00:42,791 --> 00:00:45,041
We'll be arriving shortly, Master.

2
00:00:45,125 --> 00:00:47,455
Set us down well clear of the village.

3
00:00:47,541 --> 00:00:49,381
Tensions are high enough.

4
00:00:49,458 --> 00:00:50,458
Yes, Master.

5
00:01:23,250 --> 00:01:26,380
[CREATURES WARBLE]

6
00:01:43,333 --> 00:01:45,083
[DROID BEEPS]

7
00:01:47,583 --> 00:01:48,583
[BEEPING]

8
00:02:00,416 --> 00:02:01,996
[INSECTS BUZZING]

9
00:02:07,416 --> 00:02:09,166
[MOUSE SQUEAKING]

10
00:02:12,916 --> 00:02:17,246
[BARKING]

11
00:02:19,208 --> 00:02:20,378
[VILLAGER WHISTLES]

12
00:02:20,458 --> 00:02:23,458
[DOG GROANS]

13
00:02:23,541 --> 00:02:25,541
Excuse me. Sorry to trouble y...

14
00:02:29,958 --> 00:02:31,668
[CREATURES WARBLE]

15
00:02:33,208 --> 00:02:38,288
[BEEPING]

16
00:02:43,041 --> 00:02:44,711
[WHINES]

17
00:02:51,375 --> 00:02:57,075
[BEEPING]

18
00:03:01,875 --> 00:03:04,875
[VILLAGER COUGHING]

19
00:03:08,833 --> 00:03:10,293
[DOOKU] Where is the child?

20
00:03:13,500 --> 00:03:16,960
Where are they holding the Senator's son?

21
00:03:18,208 --> 00:03:20,038
Why should we tell you?

22
00:03:32,875 --> 00:03:35,285
Allow me to make my intentions clear.

23
00:03:41,125 --> 00:03:42,325
Jedi.

24
00:03:43,250 --> 00:03:46,880
We are here to help resolve the situation.

25
00:03:48,125 --> 00:03:49,245
For the Senator.

26
00:03:49,958 --> 00:03:50,958
For everyone.

27
00:03:53,625 --> 00:03:55,825
What do you know of Senator Dagonet?

28
00:03:56,916 --> 00:04:00,206
He is one of the longest-standing
Senators in the Republic.

29
00:04:00,291 --> 00:04:04,001
Yes, and when you entered this village,
you could see the effects

30
00:04:04,083 --> 00:04:06,383
of his long-standing policies.

31
00:04:07,416 --> 00:04:11,996
With due respect, if you don't like him,
why not elect a new Senator?

32
00:04:13,875 --> 00:04:16,035
I wish it were that simple.

33
00:04:20,708 --> 00:04:24,708
Perhaps, in the beginning,
Senator Dagonet was a good person

34
00:04:24,791 --> 00:04:28,791
and had the interests
of the people in mind. But now...

35
00:04:30,791 --> 00:04:34,251
Come, I will show you
where the Senator's son is.

36
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:37,540
You're one of the kidnappers?

37
00:04:45,708 --> 00:04:47,038
They all are.

38
00:05:06,833 --> 00:05:10,673
[CREATURES WARBLE]

39
00:05:22,333 --> 00:05:24,293
[DROID CHATTERS]

40
00:05:29,250 --> 00:05:30,790
[CHATTERS]

41
00:05:44,916 --> 00:05:46,786
Have you been treated well?

42
00:05:46,875 --> 00:05:48,955
For a prisoner, yes.

43
00:05:49,666 --> 00:05:52,076
Besides, I have Two-ton here
to keep me company.

44
00:05:52,166 --> 00:05:54,076
[CHATTERS]

45
00:05:55,375 --> 00:05:56,785
Your ordeal will soon be over.

46
00:05:57,708 --> 00:05:59,168
It's not much of an ordeal.

47
00:05:59,791 --> 00:06:01,921
Not compared to how
these people are living.

48
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:06,420
And you were not aware
of these conditions?

49
00:06:06,500 --> 00:06:08,960
I rarely leave the capital.

50
00:06:09,041 --> 00:06:11,791
When I do, I spend time
off-world on Coruscant,

51
00:06:11,875 --> 00:06:13,075
not here.

52
00:06:15,708 --> 00:06:18,208
How could my father allow this
to happen to his people?

53
00:06:19,583 --> 00:06:21,383
You don't blame them for abducting you?

54
00:06:21,458 --> 00:06:23,288
What choice did they have?

55
00:06:28,125 --> 00:06:31,705
The Senator, he's here!
And he's brought soldiers.

56
00:06:32,916 --> 00:06:36,166
You have deceived us, Master Jedi.

57
00:06:36,250 --> 00:06:40,210
No, our coming here
was not known to the Senator.

58
00:06:49,166 --> 00:06:50,706
[TWO-TON CHATTERS]

59
00:07:09,166 --> 00:07:10,456
[DROID CHATTERS]

60
00:07:14,291 --> 00:07:16,001
She is hungry.

61
00:07:16,833 --> 00:07:18,503
Many would do the same.

62
00:07:20,166 --> 00:07:25,536
Jedi, arrest these criminals
and have them release my son at once.

63
00:07:26,208 --> 00:07:30,668
I'm afraid our investigation
is not yet complete, Senator.

64
00:07:30,750 --> 00:07:32,670
Investigation?

65
00:07:33,708 --> 00:07:36,128
They abducted my son.

66
00:07:36,208 --> 00:07:38,168
I demand his release!

67
00:07:39,541 --> 00:07:43,331
Let me assure you
your son is in no immediate danger.

68
00:07:44,375 --> 00:07:46,745
I'll be the judge of that.

69
00:07:46,833 --> 00:07:47,833
Guards!

70
00:08:07,333 --> 00:08:09,833
Step aside, Jedi.

71
00:08:10,750 --> 00:08:12,330
We cannot.

72
00:08:13,125 --> 00:08:15,245
You serve the Senate.

73
00:08:15,875 --> 00:08:17,165
No.

74
00:08:17,250 --> 00:08:20,130
We serve the people of this Republic.

75
00:08:23,375 --> 00:08:25,035
So be it.

76
00:08:25,125 --> 00:08:26,625
Ready!

77
00:08:34,041 --> 00:08:35,291
Aim!

78
00:08:42,041 --> 00:08:43,131
Stand down.

79
00:08:43,666 --> 00:08:45,786
I will not.

80
00:08:54,583 --> 00:08:56,173
Fire!

81
00:09:10,166 --> 00:09:12,076
[GRUNTS, SCREAMS]

82
00:09:12,166 --> 00:09:13,166
[SENATOR'S SON] No!

83
00:09:24,500 --> 00:09:25,500
[GRUNTS]

84
00:09:30,958 --> 00:09:32,288
Halt!

85
00:09:56,541 --> 00:09:59,421
I will destroy this town

86
00:09:59,500 --> 00:10:03,130
and make an example of it,
and many others.

87
00:10:04,666 --> 00:10:06,576
None shall defy me!

88
00:10:06,666 --> 00:10:09,246
Not even you, Master Jed...

89
00:10:09,333 --> 00:10:10,713
[FORCE RUMBLING]

90
00:10:13,625 --> 00:10:17,035
[CHOKING]

91
00:10:17,666 --> 00:10:18,706
Master.

92
00:10:31,500 --> 00:10:32,960
[SCREAMS]

93
00:10:35,916 --> 00:10:37,456
Go! Save your father.

94
00:10:37,541 --> 00:10:39,081
- What?
- Go now.

95
00:10:41,375 --> 00:10:44,785
- Corruption like yours must be eradicated.
- [CHOKING]

96
00:10:45,500 --> 00:10:46,500
No!

97
00:10:47,250 --> 00:10:48,500
Stop!

98
00:10:49,625 --> 00:10:51,575
Master, it's over.

99
00:10:51,666 --> 00:10:53,496
[CHOKING]

100
00:10:55,166 --> 00:10:56,626
- [GROANS]
- [LIGHTSABER RETRACTS]

101
00:10:58,916 --> 00:11:01,666
[COUGHS]

102
00:11:01,750 --> 00:11:02,750
My son.

103
00:11:07,333 --> 00:11:10,383
Father, how could you do this?

104
00:11:11,125 --> 00:11:12,285
These are your people...

105
00:11:14,666 --> 00:11:16,126
our people!

106
00:11:37,583 --> 00:11:40,083
I will not allow
your suffering to continue.

107
00:11:41,166 --> 00:11:42,376
I promise.

108
00:12:19,708 --> 00:12:21,878
[BARKING]

109
00:12:32,000 --> 00:12:35,500
I wonder if any meaningful change
will come of this.

110
00:12:36,875 --> 00:12:39,035
Is that why you took action
into your own hands?

111
00:12:40,875 --> 00:12:43,785
Your actions saved many lives today.

112
00:12:44,458 --> 00:12:46,248
Just thinking in the moment, Master.

113
00:12:47,625 --> 00:12:49,165
Well, then.

114
00:12:49,250 --> 00:12:52,710
You're a much wiser man than I,
Qui-Gon Jinn.

115
00:12:53,708 --> 00:12:54,958
Thanks to your teachings.

